{"tid":2463536,"cid":21,"subCid":8,"title":"【唔計edm】有冇人係聽開流行(廣義)內嘅純音樂?","createTime":"2021-03-26T18:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T18:56:06.000Z","uid":193548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c27d44258ed24f87c387da7da098690f7f8de4cf","tid":2463536,"uid":193548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T18:54:45.000Z","msg":"因聽器樂 所以就開喺樂器分台<br />\n唔知有冇同好分享吓啲曲目？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n放幾首推廣吓純音樂先<br />\nTomoya Naka嘅 Berceau，好普通無乜特別嘅鋼琴作品，純粹好聽。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5wFu-Alohrs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5wFu-Alohrs&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWq%2BFBM5c0LZ9Ts2TrilmEa4%3D&h=c605d097\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5wFu-Alohrs</a><br />\n<br />\nAkira kosemura嘅light dance 同上面一樣可以輕鬆聽嘅鋼琴作品，後面高潮享部份真係好正。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YmWH1hL5cd8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYmWH1hL5cd8&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWq%2BFBM5c0LZ9Ts2TrilmEa4%3D&h=db6ab379\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YmWH1hL5cd8</a><br />\n<br />\n悲しい決意 聽落有啲啲憂鬱感嘅曲目。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/J2MlAFTbbFI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJ2MlAFTbbFI&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWq%2BFBM5c0LZ9Ts2TrilmEa4%3D&h=c580aabd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/J2MlAFTbbFI</a><br />\n<br />\nCicada 台灣樂團，琴同弦嘅室內樂，哩首breakaway 唔知點解聽完有種壓力得以釋放嘅感覺<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uhI67DaKWsU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuhI67DaKWsU&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWq%2BFBM5c0LZ9Ts2TrilmEa4%3D&h=46e773e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uhI67DaKWsU</a><br />\n<br />\n 義大利作曲家Fabrizio Paterlini 嘅soffia la notte(night breaths)，頭幾秒應該已經會令你想聽落去。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JYVXM0qNQAg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJYVXM0qNQAg&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWq%2BFBM5c0LZ9Ts2TrilmEa4%3D&h=1f088308\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JYVXM0qNQAg</a><br />\n<br />\nTom barabas 嘅visions, 鋼琴加少量弦樂同管樂嘅作品，聽落好有空間感。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vaiLlS14n1k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvaiLlS14n1k&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWq%2BFBM5c0LZ9Ts2TrilmEa4%3D&h=de050ee7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vaiLlS14n1k</a><br />\n<br />\nLudovico einaudi 嘅ancora 聽落完全係不帶情感 ，單純展現出音樂嘅美感嘅鋼琴作品。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hdSMZTSRQNc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhdSMZTSRQNc&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWq%2BFBM5c0LZ9Ts2TrilmEa4%3D&h=7240eb0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hdSMZTSRQNc</a><br />\n<br />\n最後係哩首 用生命寫故事 後搖好似係 係哩幾日搵到覺幾正嘅作品 前半聽完有種被激勵嘅感覺  但好可惜嘅係6:59後竟然開始有人聲唱。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6bMXAPKEIJs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6bMXAPKEIJs&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWq%2BFBM5c0LZ9Ts2TrilmEa4%3D&h=9fc0d654\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6bMXAPKEIJs</a><br />\n<br />\n哩啲純音樂真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知有幾多人同我一樣中意發掘哩啲純音樂作品呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"588311fe09bead7868d3a9630318e80b8976dbf6","tid":2463536,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T18:56:06.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最中2隻青蛙"}]}